cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR

The paper proposes a model to estimate tactile properties from visual perception alone, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) to interact with the environment. The model uses an encoder-decoder network, which is a common technique in deep learning (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the generalization of the model to materials not included in the training data, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
